{"title":"欢迎中国人民志愿军归国","authors":["陈毅"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎中国人民志愿军归国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军的同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们归国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们交结了朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们打败了敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们保卫了祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们拯救了和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们的功勋万古存！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军的同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们归国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们交结了朝鲜朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗中建立了深厚的友情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝鲜人是中国人的亲人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国人是朝鲜人的亲人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝友谊万古存！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军的同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们归国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们在朝鲜打败了敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们自吹百多年未打过败仗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是这一次败于朝鲜人和中国人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现代化的作战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考验出中朝军队有本领。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中朝团结万古存！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军的同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们归国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们保卫了祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的建设也支援了你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一面作战一面建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一最宝贵的经验，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说服了一切怀疑派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也最严厉的教训了敌人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，要记住："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侵略者惨遭失败。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"神圣自卫真光荣！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（五）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军的同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢迎你们归国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们制止了侵略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们拯救了和平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们不要忘记朋友，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也还要随时警惕着敌人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同志们，要有各项准备，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要居安思危，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们国土上还盘据着敌人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（六）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志愿军的同志们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们正分批回国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们热烈的来欢迎。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国建设正在大跃进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它张臂欢迎你们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要克服大自然，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你看，这是一个多么强大的敌人！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快参加这一新的战斗："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们的革命指向地球的表皮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们的革命指向天空的外层！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1958年6月"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}